Author: miapensa
Text: So many occasions where expensive vegan food that I have bought goes to waste because I don’t want the calories. Ben and Jerry’s dairy free is $12/a pint here but it sits in my freezer unopened because I can’t bring myself to eat it :(

Author: sintos-compa
Text: Our fridge starts beeping when open too long, many a time have I caught myself by that beep staring into its abyss. I read it here somewhere and now I call that behavior “the scan”
